lead_paragraph: The Houston Dynamo reached its second straight M.L.S. Cup with a 2-0 victory last night over visiting Kansas City in the Western Conference final. Nate Jaqua and Dwayne De Rosario scored for Houston, which will face the New England Revolution next Sunday in a rematch of last year’s title match.
